					<h2>Our Mission</h2>				
					<h5>To advance the fields of procurement, supply chain, e-commerce, and tourism management by promoting excellence in education, research, and professional practice. AAPSCM is committed to fostering innovation, ethical standards, and global collaboration to empower professionals and organizations to navigate the complexities of a dynamic world.</h5>				
															<img width="64" height="64" src="https://aapscm.org/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/shared-vision.png" alt="" />															
