		<p>Are you interested in pursuing procurement, supply chain, e-commerce, or tourism opportunities in the United States? <strong>AAPSCM®</strong> has been recognized for three consecutive years as one of the “fastest-growing professional associations in the State of South Carolina,” offering a range of quick job search and career advancement possibilities. To learn more about our current opportunities, please email <strong>info@aapscm.org</strong>. We are also expanding our global footprint by approving authorized training partners in the Middle East, India, China, and Africa. If your organization is interested in becoming an affiliate partner, we invite you to reach out at <strong>admin@aapscm.org</strong>. Join us and be part of a dynamic, rapidly growing network shaping the future of these critical industries.</p>		
